data.description: Beautiful almost new construction home in the fast growing community of Apison.  Hardwood flooring throughout the main level of the home.  Living room is centered around a stone fireplace with built-ins and coffered ceilings.  Living room has tons of natural light flowing in and open to the kitchen.  Kitchen has lots of cabinetry with centered island, perfect for cooking meals and entertaining at the same time.  Kitchen island has granite countertops and farmhouse sink.  Wonderful storage and large walk-in pantry.  Kitchen has stainless appliances, gas stove and convection oven.  Center island offers a bar area for those meals on the go and there is an eat-in dining area also.  Off the kitchen you will find a gorgeous sunroom that is heated/cooled and overlooks the large flat backyard.  The primary suite is on the main level of the home and is very large with pan ceiling, hardwood floors, den area that makes a perfect office, exercise room or TV viewing area.  The primary bathroom is so luxurious with specialty tile throughout.  Granite countertops, double bowl vanities, walk-in closet and the most amazing two person walk-in shower.   On the main level of the home, you will also find two other bedrooms that share a full bathroom, which gives perfect access to the kitchen for a guest room or a baby's room.  There is also half bathroom for guests on the main level and the laundry room with custom cabinetry.  Upstairs you will find a wonderfully large bedroom and an oversized bonus room that share a full hallway bathroom and a great kitchenette area.  Perfect as a teenager or in-law suite area of the home.  Or even a home theater room with a bar area.  The home has neutral colors throughout and a 3 car garage.  The yard is a great size for entertaining guests.  Prairie Pass Subdivision has a community pool area and has sidewalks throughout.  Call today to schedule your own private viewing of this wonderful home!
